					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Another reason to initialize the stack pointer is if you transfer it to the X register (TSX) and access previously pushed values using different base addresses ($0101, $0102, $0103 and so on). If the stack pointer has wrapped around, that won't work.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

